name: PlatinumGoodies
overview:
PlatinumGoodies.com is your wedding favors superstore.

PlatinumGoodies is your one-stop shop for unique favors and party essentials for all your special occasions. Inside the store you will find a wide variety of unique wedding favors, including candles, coasters and wine stoppers. Additionally, in our Party Essential Department you will find cake toppers, boxes/bags for your favors, place cards and place card holders as well as other table decor items. You will also find favors broken out into themes such as beach, by season and most importantly ethnic.

PlatinumGoodies specializes in providing distinctive, ethnic selections from all around the world. We work with artists to handcraft brass statues that will make your favors unforgettable.
